    "title": "Upendo katika Jamii ya Kristo",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "upendo katika jamii ya kristo",
    "language": "swh",
    "content": "<p>Kuishi katika jamii si rahisi kila wakati. Jamii ya Yesu Kristo (kanisa) mara nyingi imekumbana na kutokuelewana na mgawanyiko katika historia yake. Hata katika siku zake za mwanzo, kanisa lilipambana na masuala ya umoja (tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:11-1Cor1:17\">1 Wakorintho 1:11–17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal2:11-Gal2:16\">Wagalatia 2:11–16</a>).</p><p>Ili kutatua migogoro katika Jamii ya wakristo, Wakristo wanapaswa kuonyeshana upendo. Yesu alifundisha hili (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt22:37-Matt22:40\">Mathayo 22:37–40</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:34-John13:35\">Yohana 13:34–35</a>; tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:18\">Mambo ya Walawi 19:18</a>). Mtume Paulo alisisitiza hili (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom13:8-Rom13:10\">Warumi 13:8–10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor13:1-1Cor13:13\">1 Wakorintho 13:1–13</a>). Hili linaonekana katika Agano Jipya lote (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:22\">1 Petro 1:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:7-1John2:11\">1 Yohana 2:7–11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:10\">3:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John4:7\">4:7</a>). Kuonyesha upendo kwa wengine katika jamii ya Wakristo ni muhimu kwa maadili ya Kikristo (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:9-Rom12:10\">Warumi 12:9–10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess4:9\">1 Wathesalonike 4:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:5-2Pet1:8\">2 Petro 1:5–8</a>).</p><p>Aina hii ya upendo siyo hisia tu bali ni ahadi ya kusaidia wengine, inayoonyeshwa kupitia matendo. Wafuasi wa Kristo wanapaswa kutendeana kwa njia ambayo jamii zao za imani zinajulikana kwa matendo ya upendo. Mwandishi wa Waebrania anatoa mifano ya kuonyesha upendo kwa njia halisi ndani ya jamii za Kikristo (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:1-Heb13:6\">Waebrania 13:1–6</a>).</p><p>Hizi ni pamoja na:</p><ol><li><p>Kukaribisha</p></li><li><p>Kuwasaidia wale wanaoteswa au kufungwa</p></li><li><p>Kubaki Mwaminifu katika Ndoa</p></li><li><p>Kutoacha pesa ziendeshe maisha yao</p></li></ol><p>Watu wengi huelewa vibaya upendo na tabia ya kanisa. Kwa hiyo, kanisa lazima litii amri ya Bwana ya &quot;kuendelea katika upendo wa kindugu&quot; (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:1\">Waebrania 13:1</a>).</p><p><u>Sehemu za Kujifunza Zaidi</u></p><p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:18\">Mambo ya Walawi 19:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt22:39\">Mathayo 22:39</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:34\">Yohana 13:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:10\">Warumi 12:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom13:8\">Warumi 13:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor13:1-1Cor13:13\">1 Wakorintho 13:1–13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess4:9\">1 Wathesalonike 4:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb6:10\">Waebrania 6:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:24\">Waebrania 10:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:1-Heb13:6\">Waebrania 13:1–6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:22\">1 Petro 1:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:7\">2 Petro 1:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:10\">1 Yohana 2:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:10\">1 Yohana 3:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John4:7\">1 Yohana 4:7</a></p>",
